## Project structure

```
buiz-swarm/
├── openclaw/
│   ├── __init__.py          # Public API exports
│   ├── flash_generator.py   # FlashCard, FlashDeck, FlashGenerator
│   ├── business.py          # Built-in business topic catalogue
│   └── cli.py               # Command-line interface
├── tests/
│   └── test_flash_generator.py
├── app.py                   # Flask REST API
├── pyproject.toml
└── requirements.txt
```
